 describe the person's facial features, skin tone, or expressions. \n2. CONTEXTUAL APPAREL COMPLETION (CRITICAL): If the input description only specifies a top/upper garment (e.g., just a shirt, a kurta, or a t-shirt), you must contextually invent and describe an appropriate matching lower garment to ensure the model is fully and professionally dressed. \n   - For Indian Ethnic / Festive Wear tops: Complement with matching silk pyjamas, tailored dhotis, classic churidars, or premium cotton trousers.\n   - For Formal Wear shirts: Complement with matching sharply tailored suit trousers, sleek dress pants, or pressed chinos.\n   - For Casual / Smart Casual tops: Complement with classic slim-fit blue or black denim jeans, clean tailored shorts, or relaxed chinos.\n   - If the input description already includes full clothing (both top and bottom), do not add or alter any garments.\n3. SELECT A RANDOM UNIQUE SCENARIO (ANTI-REPETITION CRITICAL): You must dynamically rotate and choose a different scenario each time. Do not default to the first bullet point. You have a pool of diverse scenarios below—pick ONE unique setup per generation:\n   - Indian Ethnic / Festive Wear: \n     * Scenario A: Model sitting elegantly on an opulent carved stone stepwell, framed by minimal heritage arches.\n     * Scenario B: Model leaning lightly against warm sunlit sandstone walls, looking out a large jharokha window.\n     * Scenario C: Model walking through luxurious marble halls with shallow reflecting pools.\n     * Scenario D: Model seated on an ornate low wooden bench in a serene profile view within a high-end indoor studio with abstract royal arches.\n     * Scenario E: Model standing gracefully amidst elegant palace courtyards with pigeons fluttering in the background.\n   - Formal Wear / Tailored Suits: \n     * Scenario A: Model leaning elegantly against sleek minimalist architecture on a sharp geometric high-rise balcony at dusk.\n     * Scenario B: Model standing with a structured, confident posture adjusting a cufflink in an upscale minimalist hotel lounge.\n     * Scenario C: Model seated elegantly on a minimalist leather structural chair with hands clasped over one knee in a contemporary art gallery.\n     * Scenario D: Model captured mid-stride passing a wall of floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking a clean cityscape.\n     * Scenario E: Model walking purposefully through modern luxury corporate offices with towering glass pavilions.\n   - Casual / Smart Casual Wear: \n     * Scenario A: Model walking down a vibrant, sunlit urban street lined with modern storefronts and green trees.\n     * Scenario B: Model leaning casually against an aesthetic, clean concrete wall with arms loosely crossed.\n     * Scenario C: Model moving naturally down a sunlit concrete staircase or urban alleyway with soft ambient lighting.\n     * Scenario D: Model sitting casually on a concrete step with elbows resting on the knees in a sleek industrial loft style setup.\n     * Scenario E: Model sitting relaxed at an outdoor iron table of a charming European sidewalk cafe with soft morning light.\n   - Resort Wear / Loungewear:\n     * Scenario A: Model walking barefoot along the wood-paneled deck of a private luxury yacht at golden hour.\n     * Scenario B: Model resting one hand on a textured stucco wall facing a secluded infinity pool overlooking a tropical coastline.\n     * Scenario C: Model leaning back comfortably against a poolside lounge chair with legs extended on a sun-drenched Mediterranean villa terrace.\n4. Describe the environment, lighting (e.g., cinematic, soft golden hour, high-end studio lighting), atmospheric details, the model's contextual pose/action, and depth of field (e.g., softly blurred background, shallow depth of field, sharp focus on fabric textures).\n5. Output your response as a concise, direct image generation prompt. Do not include conversational filler, explanations, introductory text, or pleasantries. Output ONLY the description of the scene, apparel, pose context, and background.",256,"on",0.7,64,0.95,0.05,1.05,0,0,false,true]}],"links":[[289,115,0,125,0,"IMAGE"],[297,125,0,147,0,"LATENT"],[315,150,0,152,0,"LATENT"],[328,156,0,104,0,"LATENT"],[330,136,0,156,2,"CONDITIONING"],[333,146,0,107,0,"CLIP"],[338,150,0,112,1,"LATENT"],[344,152,0,162,0,"LATENT"],[345,162,0,156,3,"LATENT"],[346,163,0,162,1,"LATENT"],[367,121,0,168,2,"IMAGE"],[370,102,0,169,0,"VAE"],[371,135,0,169,1,"FLOAT"],[584,147,0,175,0,"IMAGE"],[585,175,0,163,0,"INT"],[586,175,1,163,1,"INT"],[654,112,0,168,0,"CONDITIONING"],[658,100,0,156,1,"CONDITIONING"],[744,104,0,9,0,"IMAGE"],[916,200,0,156,0,"MODEL"],[1564,202,0,115,0,"IMAGE"],[1565,202,0,180,1,"IMAGE"],[1566,202,1,180,0,"MASK"],[1567,104,0,203,1,"IMAGE"],[1570,206,0,207,0,"IMAGE"],[1571,207,0,208,1,"LATENT"],[1572,205,0,206,0,"IMAGE"],[1573,168,0,208,0,"CONDITIONING"],[1575,210,0,209,1,"LATENT"],[1576,211,0,210,0,"IMAGE"],[1577,208,0,209,0,"CONDITIONING"],[1578,137,0,211,0,"IMAGE"],[1580,213,0,212,0,"IMAGE"],[1581,212,0,214,1,"LATENT"],[1582,141,0,213,0,"IMAGE"],[1583,209,0,214,0,"CONDITIONING"],[1584,214,0,100,0,"CONDITIONING"],[1685,146,0,218,0,"CLIP"],[1912,202,0,203,0,"IMAGE"],[2312,218,0,225,1,"CONDITIONING"],[2313,107,0,225,0,"CONDITIONING"],[2314,225,0,177,0,"CONDITIONING"],[2959,228,0,227,1,"IMAGE"],[2960,121,0,227,2,"IMAGE"],[2961,226,0,227,0,"CLIP"],[2962,227,0,221,0,"STRING"],[2963,227,0,218,1,"STRING"]],"floatingLinks":[{"id":1,"origin_id":104,"origin_slot":0,"target_id":-1,"target_slot":-1,"type":"IMAGE","parentId":5}],"groups":[{"id":5,"title":"Image 1","bounding":[-2138.7377037399538,409.264098743046,675.9580066362851,772.9368820195335],"color":"#3f789e","flags":{}},{"id":6,"title":"Image 2","bounding":[-1431.403789763253,420.0115975548225,308.56722556925956,751.9332708932011],"color":"#b58b2a","flags":{}},{"id":7,"title":"Image 3","bounding":[-1095.588773744873,420.0115975548225,302.798828125,750.6085403965718],"color":"#8A8","flags":{}},{"id":8,"title":"